\begin_layout Subsection*

\lang english
1.
 Purpose
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\lang english
This policy establishes the mandatory governance framework for classifying and protecting Elko County data assets.
 This policy mandates data stewardship,
 classification assignment,
 and security attribute association while preserving statutory transparency obligations under Nevada law.
\end_layout

