\end_deeper

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize

\series bold
\lang english
IT Director
\series default
:
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize

\lang english
Shall serve as the primary governance authority for data classification and data security.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\lang english
Shall define and enforce the County Data Classification Schema and mandatory safeguards.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\lang english
Shall designate the Local Agency Security Officer (LASO) in writing and shall register the designation with the CJIS Systems Agency (currently Nevada Department of Public Safety).
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\lang english
Shall serve as the Information Operations Records Custodian under Board delegation for Information Operations records and IT-managed data assets,
 including retention and disposition procedures.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\lang english
Shall ensure required technical controls,
 handling standards,
 and exception decisions are implemented and enforced County-wide for County-managed systems.
\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize

\series bold
\lang english
Local Agency Security Officer (LASO)
