\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\lang english
Shall maintain CJIS security documentation,
 including system configuration data,
 and shall support CJIS compliance audits of hardware and procedures.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\lang english
Shall disseminate CJIS information security alerts and related material to County stakeholders with CJI access.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\lang english
Shall keep the CSA informed of information security needs and incidents.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\lang english
Shall authorize or deny requests to reclassify Restricted CJI downward,
 subject to any additional CJIS governing authority required by applicable agreements.
\end_layout

