\series bold
\lang english
Storage,
 Media Control,
 and Disposal
\series default
:
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize

\lang english
All Information Operations Personnel shall protect Confidential and Restricted data through secure storage controls.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\lang english
All Information Operations Personnel shall ensure data is destroyed or sanitized when no longer required,
 consistent with the retention requirements defined in Section 6.9 and the sanitization procedures defined in 
