The responsible Department Head for each category.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\lang english
Logical and physical storage locations,
 including approved cloud services.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\lang english
Applicable retention requirements based on mandatory Nevada retention schedules and County directives.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\lang english
The IT Director shall review and update the Data Inventory annually and following significant changes to systems,
 services,
 or regulatory obligations.
 The Data Inventory shall support the System Inventory maintained under 
